\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=6cd512b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=731bb656\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=70de9358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"b8785009d4822d13baca3d6e63d80c63a3c8984f","tid":1742813,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/h93TUgu.gif\" /><br />\n今日係1121, 721<strong>元朗恐襲</strong>之後第4個月!"},{"pid":"f2dca058115494a544932db6185176784fcaf121","tid":1742813,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6738f96b61bf74d11f4b200bd7d5c302fadafa04","tid":1742813,"uid":389,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:59:55.000Z","msg":"我個number夠細未？<br />\n<br />\n篤灰蘋果垃撚圾"},{"pid":"13b3ee4d258b5a87ace5cb5b6cbdc96061874861","tid":1742813,"uid":306826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:00:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">星期日記住投票</span></span><br />\n阻你地少少時間 有關選舉問題可以睇以下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0成本截斷建制藍絲收入 (下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\